ent-SelectWerewolfFormAction = Select form
.desc = Choose the coloration of your werewolf form.

ent-LycantropyProgressMenuAction = Evolution menu
.desc = Open the evolution menu.

ent-LycantropyHowlAction = Howl
.desc = Emit a howl audible to everyone on the map, in exchange for minor health regeneration.

ent-WerewolfInfectAction = Infection
.desc = Toggle infection mode. In infection mode, your bites will transmit lycanthropy to humanoids in critical condition.

ent-WerewolfHealAlliesAction = Heal allies
.desc = Help nearby werewolves, healing them.

ent-WerewolfRegenAction = Regeneration
.desc = Restore a part of your health.

ent-WerewolfHotBloodAction = Hot blood
.desc = Increase your speed for a short time.

ent-WerewolfHuntAction = Blood hunt
.desc = Eliminate stamina damage from lunging.

ent-WerewolfMoonAction = Lunar rage
.desc = Temporarily stop receiving stamina damage and slightly increase your speed.

ent-WerewolfTearingAction = Rending maw
.desc = Your next attack deals extra damage and knocks back the target.

ent-WerewolfDashAction = Shadow lunge
.desc = Your next lunge will stun the first target you collide with.

ent-WerewolfBloodFeelAction = Blood sense
.desc = Track your victims by the scent of blood.

ent-PolymorphWerewolfAction = Transformation
.desc = Transform into a werewolf at any time.

ent-RevertPolymorphWerewolfAction = Transformation
.desc = Transform back to your original self.